<p>Gets the size of any unused space around the text.</p>


<pre class="language-csharp"><code class="language-csharp">public SkiaSharp.SKRect MeasuredPadding { get; }</code></pre>

<h2 id="remarks">Remarks</h2><p>If MaxWidth is not set, the left and right padding will always be zero.</p>
<p>This property also returns a bottom padding amount if MaxHeight is set.</p>
<p>The returned top padding is always zero.</p>
<p>The return rectangle describes padding amounts for each edge - not
rectangle co-ordinates.</p>

